commit.message: Prepare for the next release candidate

Only set POSIX permissions if needed

Only callers of PathUtils.setPosixPermissions(...) are affected:

- PathUtils.setReadOnly(...)
- PathUtils.deleteFile(..., DeleteOption...)
- CleaningPathVisitor
- DeletingPathVisitor

Passes on macOS, fails on Linux and Windows with AccessDeniedException.

- Better comment
- Bullet-proof old test for re-runs
